@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam roundCorner 15
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
[*] --> Reviewed
Reviewed --> Pending : process
Pending --> Created : reject
Pending : entry / log tracking
Created --> Archived : submit
Archived --> Rejected : submit
Archived : entry / log tracking
Rejected --> Active : cancel
Active --> Rejected : revert
Active --> [*]
@enduml